  --divider-width: 100%;\n}\n<\/style>\n\t<\/section>\n\t\n\t<section class=\"section\" id=\"section_715940430\">\n\t\t<div class=\"bg section-bg fill bg-fill  bg-loaded\" >\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\t\n\n\t\t<div class=\"section-content relative\">\n\t\t\t\n<div class=\"row\"  id=\"row-2050241752\">\n\n\t<div id=\"col-1212908823\" class=\"col small-12 large-12\"  data-animate=\"fadeInUp\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-inner\"  >\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t<div id=\"text-636800418\" class=\"text\">\n\t\t\n<h4>EXPERIENCE MEETS RESEARCH<\/h4>\n<p>Doing business worldwide comes with a great number of advantages: more opportunities, new markets, and greater business growth. However, this development means you might also find yourself trying to recover money from a customer who is not only in a different time zone to you but also has different laws to abide by.<\/p>\n<p>Although in this situation you may worry you have to write the money off as irrecoverable, we can give you confidence in the knowledge that your international debt recovery options don\u2019t diminish as soon as the debt crosses borders.<\/p>\n<p>To find out more about the IFPC pricing structure, you need to get familiar with the International pricing guide.<\/p>\n\t\t\n<style>\n#text-636800418 {\n  text-align: center;\n}\n<\/style>\n\t<\/div>\n\t\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\n<style>\n#col-1212908823 > .col-inner {\n  padding: 0px 5% 0px 5%;\n}\n@media (min-width:550px) {\n  #col-1212908823 > .col-inner {\n    padding: 0px 20% 0px 20%;\n  }\n}\n<\/style>\n\t<\/div>\n\n\t\n<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\t\n<style>\n#section_715940430 {\n  padding-top: 30px;\n  padding-bottom: 30px;\n}\n#section_715940430 .ux-shape-divider--top svg {\n  height: 150px;\n  --divider-top-width: 100%;\n}\n#section_715940430 .ux-shape-divider--bottom svg {\n  height: 150px;\n  --divider-width: 100%;\n}\n@media (min-width:550px) {\n  #section_715940430 {\n    padding-top: 100px;\n    padding-bottom: 100px;\n  }\n}\n<\/style>\n\t<\/section>\n\t\n\t<section class=\"section\" id=\"section_135311555\">\n\t\t<div class=\"bg section-bg fill bg-fill  bg-loaded\" >\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\t\n\n\t\t<div class=\"section-content relative\">\n\t\t\t\n<div class=\"row\"  id=\"row-284435620\">\n\n\t<div id=\"col-1950626557\" class=\"col small-12 large-12\"  data-animate=\"fadeInRight\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-inner\"  >\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t<div id=\"text-1526973153\" class=\"text\">\n\t\t\n<h3 class=\"uppercase\">HOW IT WORKS<\/h3>\n\t\t\n<style>\n#text-1526973153 {\n  text-align: center;\n}\n<\/style>\n\t<\/div>\n\t\n\t<div id=\"gap-109572675\" class=\"gap-element clearfix\" style=\"display:block; height:auto;\">\n\t\t\n<style>\n#gap-109572675 {\n  padding-top: 30px;\n}\n<\/style>\n\t<\/div>\n\t\n\n\t\t<div class=\"tabbed-content\">\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<ul class=\"nav nav-line nav-vertical nav-uppercase nav-size-normal nav-left\"><li class=\"tab active has-icon\"><a href=\"#tab_no-collection,-no-fees\"><span>NO COLLECTION, NO FEES<\/span><\/a><\/li>\n<li class=\"tab has-icon\"><a href=\"#tab_research\"><span>RESEARCH<\/span><\/a><\/li>\n<li class=\"tab has-icon\"><a href=\"#tab_contact\"><span>CONTACT<\/span><\/a><\/li>\n<li class=\"tab has-icon\"><a href=\"#tab_funds-transfer\"><span>FUNDS TRANSFER<\/span><\/a><\/li><\/ul><div class=\"tab-panels\"><div class=\"panel active entry-content\" id=\"tab_no-collection,-no-fees\">\n<p>This is a risk free service \u2013 If successful we charge a percentage commission based on your client\u2019s location. If we are unsuccessful, you will pay nothing.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"panel entry-content\" id=\"tab_research\">\n<p>We research the history of the debt and any contractual issues that may be compromising payment. We also gather information about your customer and identify key personnel who may authorise payment.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"panel entry-content\" id=\"tab_contact\">\n<p>We then attempt to establish contact with the correct personnel within the debtor company directly by telephone, letter and email to press your claim and negotiate payment.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"panel entry-content\" id=\"tab_funds-transfer\">\n<p>When your payment has been recovered we send the money directly into your company bank account.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\n<style>\n#col-1950626557 > .col-inner {\n  padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;\n}\n<\/style>\n\t<\/div>\n\n\t\n<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\t\n<style>\n#section_135311555 {\n  padding-top: 30px;\n  padding-bottom: 30px;\n  background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\n}\n#section_135311555 .ux-shape-divider--top svg {\n  height: 150px;\n  --divider-top-width: 100%;\n}\n#section_135311555 .ux-shape-divider--bottom svg {\n  height: 150px;\n  --divider-width: 100%;\n}\n<\/style>\n\t<\/section>\n\t\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"page-blank.php","meta":{"footnotes":""},"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/ifp.center\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/36"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/ifp.center\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/ifp.center\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/ifp.center\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/ifp.center\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=36"}],"version-history":[{"count":77,"href":"https:\/\/ifp.center\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/36\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":724,"href":"https:\/\/ifp.center\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/36\/revisions\/724"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/ifp.center\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=36"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}